wordpressPost.title: Øya 2019 is sold out!
wordpressPost.excerpt: We are looking forward to getting started.
wordpressPost.content:
One week before the festival area opens, Ticketmaster has sold the last Øya tickets. Our volunteers have already started working on the beautiful site. We are looking forward to welcoming audience, artists, partners and even more volunteers.

See you in Tøyenparken next week!
